  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Phaser<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Research Preference: Power and Shields<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Lemeresh</span> are almost =
ethereal
  in appearance. They are large <span class=3DGramE>water based</span> life
  forms.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Lemeresh</span> live in the=
 deepest
  oceans of a planet, under the water they build leviathan like ships with
  extremely powerful weaponry.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Little is known about the <span class=3DSpellE>Lemer=
esh</span>
  outside of their appearance and observing their <span class=3DSpellE><span
  class=3DGramE>under water</span></span> ships. They are insular and secre=
tive,
  a race of very few words that does not share any information about themse=
lves
  with others.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Most races fear that if the <span class=3DSpellE>Lem=
eresh</span>
  are able to somehow convert the full array of their aquatic-based technol=
ogy
  to the vastness of space, they will be unequalled in power.</p>
